<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Project Sentinel - Predictive Coastal Defense</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        /* --- Global Theme & Base Styles --- */
        :root {
            --sentinel-green: #4CAF50;
            --sentinel-blue: #2196F3;
            --sentinel-teal: #009688;
            --dark-bg: #1a1a1a;
            --medium-bg: #242424;
            --light-text: #f0f0f0;
            --medium-text: #ccc;
            --dark-text: #aaa;
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--dark-bg);
            color: var(--light-text);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        /* --- Header --- */
        .header {
            background-color: rgba(36, 36, 36, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            padding: 15px 0;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .header.scrolled {
            padding: 10px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .header.container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 1.8em;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--sentinel-green);
            text-decoration: none;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .logo i {
            margin-right: 8px;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.1); }
            100% { transform: scale(1); }
        }

        .nav-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            width: 100%;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-grow: 1;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            color: var(--medium-text);
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 20px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .nav-links a:after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 0;
            height: 2px;
            bottom: -5px;
            left: 0;
            background-color: var(--sentinel-green);
            transition: width 0.3s ease;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: var(--light-text);
        }

        .nav-links a:hover:after {
            width: 100%;
        }

        .nav-buttons {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .nav-buttons .btn {
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            display: inline-block;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.95em;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, transparent, transparent);
            border: 2px solid var(--sentinel-green);
            color: var(--sentinel-green);
            margin-right: 15px;
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--sentinel-green), #45a049);
            color: white;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 7px 14px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--sentinel-green), #45a049);
            color: white;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #45a049, var(--sentinel-green));
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 7px 14px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.4);
        }

        .btn i {
            margin-right: 8px;
        }

        /* --- Hero Section --- */
        .hero {
            padding-top: 180px;
            padding-bottom: 120px;
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.85), rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.95)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1561470508-91e27145a4a4?q=80&w=2070') no-repeat center center/cover;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero:before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.1), transparent 70%);
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3.5em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: var(--light-text);
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease;
        }

        .hero .highlight {
            color: var(--sentinel-green);
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .hero .highlight:after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 8px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--sentinel-green), transparent);
            opacity: 0.7;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: var(--medium-text);
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto 40px;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease 0.2s both;
        }

        .hero-buttons {
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease 0.4s both;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .hero-btn {
            padding: 16px 32px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero-btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--sentinel-green), #45a049);
            color: white;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
        }

        .hero-btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.4);
        }

        .hero-btn-secondary {
            background: transparent;
            border: 2px solid var(--sentinel-green);
            color: var(--sentinel-green);
        }

        .hero-btn-secondary:hover {
            background: var(--sentinel-green);
            color: white;
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.4);
        }

        .hero-btn i {
            margin-right: 10px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        /* --- Section Styling --- */
        .section {
            padding: 100px 0;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: var(--sentinel-green);
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .section-title:after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -10px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 80px;
            height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--sentinel-green), transparent);
        }

        .section-subtitle {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: var(--medium-text);
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto 60px;
        }

        /* --- How It Works Section --- */
        .how-it-works-container {
            position: relative;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        .how-it-works-scroll {
            display: flex;
            overflow-x: auto;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
            padding: 30px 10px;
            scrollbar-width: none; /* Firefox */
            -ms-overflow-style: none; /* IE and Edge */
            gap: 25px;
        }

        .how-it-works-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar {
            display: none; /* Chrome, Safari and Opera */
        }

        .step-card {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #2a2a2a, #1f1f1f);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            z-index: 1;
            min-width: 300px;
            flex: 0 0 auto;
        }

        .step-card:before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 5px;
            height: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--sentinel-green), var(--sentinel-teal));
            transition: height 0.5s ease;
            z-index: -1;
        }

        .step-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .step-card:hover:before {
            height: 100%;
        }

        .step-number {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background-color: var(--sentinel-green);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.3);
        }

        .step-card h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 1.5em;
            color: var(--light-text);
        }

        .step-card p {
            color: var(--medium-text);
        }

        .scroll-indicator {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: var(--medium-text);
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }

        .scroll-indicator i {
            animation: bounce 2s infinite;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }

        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 20%, 50%, 80%, 100% {transform: translateX(0);}
            40% {transform: translateX(-10px);}
            60% {transform: translateX(-5px);}
        }

        /* --- Features Section --- */
        .features-section {
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #1a1a1a, #242424);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .features-section:before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='100' height='100' viewBox='0 0 100 100' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cpath d='M11 18c3.866 0 7-3.134 7-7s-3.134-7-7-7-7 3.134-7 7 3.134 7 7 7zm48 25c3.866 0 7-3.134 7-7s-3.134-7-7-7-7 3.134-7 7 3.134 7 7 7zm-43-7c1.657 0 3-1.343 3-3s-1.343-3-3-3-3 1.343-3 3 1.343 3 3 3zm63 31c1.657 0 3-1.343 3-3s-1.343-3-3-3-3 1.343-3 3 1.343 3 3 3zM34 90c1.657 0 3-1.343 3-3s-1.343-3-3-3-3 1.343-3 3 1.343 3 3 3zm56-76c1.657 0 3-1.343 3-3s-1.343-3-3-3-3 1.343-3 3 1.343 3 3 3zM12 86c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4zm28-65c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4zm23-11c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5-5 2.24-5 5 2.24 5 5 5zm-6 60c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4zm29 22c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5-5 2.24-5 5 2.24 5 5 5zM32 63c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5-5 2.24-5 5 2.24 5 5 5zm57-13c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5-5 2.24-5 5 2.24 5 5 5zm-9-21c1.105 0 2-.895 2-2s-.895-2-2-2-2 .895-2 2 .895 2 2 2zM60 91c1.105 0 2-.895 2-2s-.895-2-2-2-2 .895-2 2 .895 2 2 2zM35 41c1.105 0 2-.895 2-2s-.895-2-2-2-2 .895-2 2 .895 2 2 2zM12 60c1.105 0 2-.895 2-2s-.895-2-2-2-2 .895-2 2 .895 2 2 2z' fill='%234CAF50' fill-opacity='0.05' fill-rule='evenodd'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #2a2a2a, #1f1f1f);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-align: left;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .feature-card:before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 5px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--sentinel-green), var(--sentinel-teal));
            transform: scaleX(0);
            transform-origin: left;
            transition: transform 0.5s ease;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .feature-card:hover:before {
            transform: scaleX(1);
        }

        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            color: var(--sentinel-green);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--sentinel-green), var(--sentinel-teal));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .feature-card h3 {
            color: var(--sentinel-green);
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 1.4em;
        }

        .feature-card p {
            color: var(--medium-text);
        }

        /* --- Call to Action Section --- */
        .cta-section {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #1a1a1a, #242424);
            padding: 80px 0;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .cta-section:before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
            animation: rotate 20s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes rotate {
            from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }

        .cta-btn {
            padding: 18px 36px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--sentinel-green), #45a049);
            color: white;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
        }

        .cta-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.4);
        }

        .cta-btn i {
            margin-right: 10px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }

        /* --- Footer --- */
        .footer {
            background-color: #111;
            padding: 70px 0 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid #333;
            position: relative;
        }

        .footer:before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--sentinel-green), transparent);
        }

        .footer-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        .footer-column h4 {
            color: var(--sentinel-green);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .footer-column h4:after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -8px;
            left: 0;
            width: 40px;
            height: 2px;
            background-color: var(--sentinel-green);
        }

        .footer-column ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .footer-column li {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .footer-column a {
            color: var(--medium-text);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .footer-column a:hover {
            color: var(--sentinel-green);
            transform: translateX(5px);
        }

        .footer-bottom {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #333;
            color: var(--dark-text);
        }

        /* Responsive adjustments */
        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .nav-container {
                flex-direction: column;
                padding: 10px;
            }
            
            .nav-links {
                margin: 15px 0;
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                justify-content: center;
            }
            
            .nav-links a {
                margin: 0 10px;
            }
            
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2.8em;
            }
            
            .hero-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .header.container {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            
            .nav-links {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 10px;
            }
            
            .nav-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 10px;
                width: 100%;
            }
            
            .btn-secondary {
                margin-right: 0;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }
            
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2.2em;
            }
            
            .section {
                padding: 70px 0;
            }
            
            .section-title {
                font-size: 2em;
            }
            
            .hero-btn {
                padding: 14px 28px;
                font-size: 1em;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header class="header">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="nav-container">
                <a href="/" class="logo"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>Sentinel</a>
                <nav class="nav-links">
                    <a href="#how-it-works">How It Works</a>
                    <a href="#features">Features</a>
                    <a href="#about">About</a>
                    <a href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a>
                    <a href="/resources">Resources</a>
                </nav>
                <div class="nav-buttons">
                    <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-secondary"><i class="fas fa-tachometer-alt"></i>Manager Login</a>
                    <a href="/signup" class="btn btn-primary"><i class="fas fa-user-plus"></i>Community Signup</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="container">
                <h1>Predictive Coastal Defense for a <span class="highlight">Resilient Future</span></h1>
                <p>Project Sentinel moves beyond broad warnings to deliver precise, proactive, and actionable intelligence. We protect human lives, vital infrastructure, and our planet's blue carbon ecosystems.</p>
                <div class="hero-buttons">
                    <a href="/dashboard" class="hero-btn hero-btn-primary"><i class="fas fa-rocket"></i>Launch Manager Dashboard</a>
                    <a href="/signup" class="hero-btn hero-btn-secondary"><i class="fas fa-bell"></i>Join Community Alerts</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="how-it-works" class="section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title">From Data to Actionable Intelligence</h2>
                <p class="section-subtitle">Our multi-modal AI platform fuses real-time data to predict threats and simulate their consequences, providing unparalleled foresight and precision for coastal defense.</p>
                
                <div class="how-it-works-container">
                    <div class="how-it-works-scroll">
                        <div class="step-card">
                            <div class="step-number">1</div>
                            <h3>Real-Time Data Fusion</h3>
                            <p>The system continuously ingests high-volume data streams from diverse sources, including physical IoT sensors (tide gauges, weather stations), satellite feeds, and hyper-local weather models.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="step-card">
                            <div class="step-number">2</div>
                            <h3>AI-Powered Analysis</h3>
                            <p>Our dual-pronged AI engine uses LSTM models to detect anomalies and advanced Transformer models to forecast future threats, identifying patterns invisible to the human eye.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="step-card">
                            <div class="step-number">3</div>
                            <h3>Consequence Simulation</h3>
                            <p>This is our unique advantage. The engine doesn't just predict a storm; it simulates its specific, hyper-local impacts, answering the critical question: "So what does this mean for us?"</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="step-card">
                            <div class="step-number">4</div>
                            <h3>Actionable Alerts</h3>
                            <p>The system generates a detailed, prioritized briefing—not a simple warning. It delivers specific instructions to disaster management teams, local stakeholders, and community members via SMS and mobile notifications.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="scroll-indicator">
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-left"></i>
                        Scroll horizontally to view all features
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="features" class="section features-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title">Hyper-Local, Actionable Outputs</h2>
                <p class="section-subtitle">Our model generates a detailed impact assessment for precise locations, empowering targeted interventions and rapid response.</p>
                <div class="features-grid">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <i class="fas fa-water feature-icon"></i>
                        <h3>Inundation Maps</h3>
                        <p>Street-level flood depth predictions to visualize the exact areas at risk.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <i class="fas fa-hospital feature-icon"></i>
                        <h3>Infrastructure Risk</h3>
                        <p>Calculated risk scores for critical facilities like hospitals, power stations, and bridges.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <i class="fas fa-leaf feature-icon"></i>
                        <h3>Ecological Damage Index</h3>
                        <p>A predictive assessment of the impact on vital blue carbon ecosystems like mangroves and seagrass.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <i class="fas fa-chart-line feature-icon"></i>
                        <h3>Economic Impact Forecast</h3>
                        <p>An estimation of potential losses to local businesses, property, and key industries.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <i class="fas fa-users feature-icon"></i>
                        <h3>Human Vulnerability</h3>
                        <p>Identification of areas with high concentrations of at-risk populations and vulnerable communities.</p>
                    </div>
                     <div class="feature-card">
